🗂️ Task Manager App
______________________________________________________________________________________________________________

Task Manager App is a modern, responsive, and fully-featured productivity tool built entirely with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Manage tasks efficiently with multiple user profiles, vibrant themes, live analytics, and image exports—all locally in your browser and deployable instantly on Vercel.

⚡ Live Demo
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
👉 Experience Productivity, Simplified:
Try Task Manager App Online {https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/}
 🚀

🚀 Key Features
______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
- 🎨 Beautiful Themes: Six color palettes—Blue, Forest, Sunset, Berry, Ocean, and Rose—for a personalized look.

- 👤 Multi-User Profiles: Register, switch users, and select from 8 custom avatars.

- 📝 Comprehensive Task Management: Tasks include descriptions, priority, category, due dates, time estimates, and progress tracking.

- 🔍 Instant Filters & Sorting: Live filtering by status/category, sorting by date, priority, or alphabetical order.

- 📊 Interactive Analytics: Powered by Chart.js, see completion trends, overdue tasks, and category breakdowns.

- 🖼️ Export to Image: Download task boards or profiles as high-resolution PNGs for sharing or archiving.

- 📱 Mobile-Friendly & Accessible: Optimized for touch, keyboard navigation, and screen readers.

- 🔒 Private & Offline: All data stays local. No tracking, no cloud uploads—100% privacy.

🛠️ Tech Stack
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Technology	Purpose
HTML/CSS/JS	Core interface & application logic
Chart.js	Dynamic analytics & charts
html2canvas	Export task boards as PNG images

📦 How It Works
_________________________________________________________________________________________________
Open the live demo{https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/}
 or index.html locally.

Register a profile with your name, email, and avatar.

Add, update, and organize tasks with advanced fields.

Filter, search, and sort tasks in real time.

Export your lists or profile as a PNG image.

Manage everything offline—no login or internet required.

