📁 File Structure
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
task-manager-app/
├── index.html          # Entry point & UI
├── css/
│   └── style.css       # Theme-based styling
├── js/
│   ├── storage.js      # Local storage & multi-user persistence
│   ├── ui.js           # UI logic (charts, export, rendering)
│   └── app.js          # Core app functionality & flows
├── libs/
│   └── html2canvas.min.js # Export tasks as PNG
└── README.md           # This file

💡 Developer’s Note
_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
“Task Manager App is built for everyone—from students to professionals—to manage tasks beautifully and privately, without ads, accounts, or unnecessary complexity. Productivity should feel personal!”
— The Developer

🔭 Future Roadmap
______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
🔄 Cross-Device Sync: Secure cloud backup & Google Drive integration.

🤝 Team Collaboration: Shared lists, chat, and role-based access.

🏷️ Custom Tags: User-defined tags with color coding and advanced search.

📅 Calendar Integration: Sync tasks with Google or Apple calendars.

🔔 Notifications: Email/push alerts, reminders, and snooze features.

🧩 Third-Party Integrations: Trello, Notion, Todoist, Slack, and more.

📊 Analytics Export: CSV/PDF download for reporting or presentations.

🎮 Gamification: Points, streaks, and achievement badges to boost motivation.

